表格业务配置表的代码预览

drop table if exists MASTER_BIZ_CONFIG;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: MASTER_BIZ_CONFIG */
/*==============================================================*/
create table MASTER_BIZ_CONFIG
(
BIZ_CONFIG_CODE varchar(64) not null,
BIZ_CONFIG_NAME varchar(128) not null,
BIZ_CONFIG_VALUE varchar(256) not null,
CREATE_TIME datetime not null default CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
UPDATETIME datetime not null default CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
primary key (BIZ_CONFIG_CODE)
);
